WEBVTT

00:13:59.132 --> 00:14:01.993
kao sram kad sam sedeo ispred televizora,

00:14:02.848 --> 00:14:05.467
gledajući Pitera Dženingsa
dok najavljuje novi milenijum

00:14:05.467 --> 00:14:06.629
iznova

00:14:06.653 --> 00:14:07.803
i iznova

00:14:08.257 --> 00:14:09.407
i iznova.

00:14:09.796 --> 00:14:10.946
Nasamaren sam,

00:14:12.084 --> 00:14:13.234
izigran,

00:14:13.696 --> 00:14:14.846
prevaren.

00:14:15.403 --> 00:14:18.477
Ali ovog puta, lažni spasitelj sam bio ja.

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:23.302
Vidite, prešao sam dug put od tog oltara,

00:14:23.326 --> 00:14:25.422
te noći kad sam mislio
da će svetu doći kraj,

00:14:26.371 --> 00:14:28.576
od sveta u kom su ljudi
govorili koještarije

00:14:29.107 --> 00:14:31.745
i na patnju gledali
kao neophodnu božju datost